h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E7%BD%97%E7%8E%89%E5%A9%B7------------/" target="_blank">罗玉婷</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%9D%8E%E6%99%94------------/" target="_blank">李晔</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E7%8E%8B%E7%AB%A0%E4%BF%8A--------/" target="_blank">王章俊</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/4/" target="_blank">动漫</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86-----------/" target="_blank">大陆</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2012/" target="_blank">2012</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.08.14</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>2100年，地球能源已接近枯竭，环境污染日趋严重.. 为了实现地外星系探索计划，人类制造了名为赛尔的机器人，并建造能源探索飞船赛尔号。在宇宙探索过程中，他们还发现了外星精灵，这些精灵们成为了赛尔机器人探寻新能源的重要帮手和伙伴。而以宇宙海盗欧比组织为首的邪恶势力正在肆意掠夺宇宙资源，为了挫败他们的阴</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/97810/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/97813/" data-original="http://cj.subo8988.com:8988/upload/vod/2019-08-11/201908111565524136.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">7.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">30集全/已完结</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/97813/">赛尔号第四季</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E7%BD%97%E7%8E%89%E5%A9%B7------------/" target="_blank">罗玉婷</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E7%BF%9F%E5%B7%8D------------/" target="_blank">翟巍</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%88%98%E5%8C%97%E8%BE%B0------------/" target="_blank">刘北辰</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%9D%8E%E6%99%94------------/" target="_blank">李晔</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%AD%99%E6%99%94------------/" target="_blank">孙晔</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%90%B4%E7%A3%8A------------/" target="_blank">吴磊</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E8%83%A1%E8%B0%A6------------/" target="_blank">胡谦</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%B8%B8%E5%86%9B------------/" target="_blank">游军</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%91%A8%E5%8D%97%E9%A3%9E------------/" target="_blank">周南飞</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E4%B8%A5%E4%B8%BD%E7%A5%AF------------/" target="_blank">严丽祯</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E7%8E%8B%E6%99%93%E8%82%9C------------/" target="_blank">王晓肜</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E7%8E%8B%E7%AB%A0%E4%BF%8A--------/" target="_blank">王章俊</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/4/" target="_blank">动漫</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86-----------/" target="_blank">大陆</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2015/" target="_blank">2015</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.08.12</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>于是一年后，战神联盟齐聚赫尔卡星在SPT的协助下踏上了寻找阿瑞斯水晶的征途，途中认识了王者之剑鲁伊斯，在经历重重磨难，战神联盟终于扫平了阻碍，战胜了也想染指水晶的海盗和邪恶精灵哈迪斯，最终在一场公平的对决后，雷伊赢得了阿瑞斯水晶，帮助赛小息他们找回了无尽能源 [2]&nbsp;&nbsp;</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/97813/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/97812/" data-original="http://cj.subo8988.com:8988/upload/vod/2019-08-11/201908111565523962.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">4.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">30集全/已完结</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/97812/">赛尔号第三季</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E7%BD%97%E7%8E%89%E5%A9%B7------------/" target="_blank">罗玉婷</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E7%8E%8B%E7%AB%A0%E4%BF%8A--------/" target="_blank">王章俊</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/4/" target="_blank">动漫</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86-----------/" target="_blank">大陆</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2014/" target="_blank">2014</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.08.12</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>公元2110年，地球能源枯竭，次品赛尔机器人赛小息在光系精灵米咔的帮助下，带着成为最伟大星际探险员的梦想，和修理型赛尔机器人卡璐璐，战斗型机器人阿铁打组成了赛尔先锋战斗小队，一起登上赛尔号驶向茫茫宇宙，开始了寻找传说中看守着无尽能源的雷伊的冒险&nbsp;</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/97812/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/97811/" data-original="http://cj.subo8988.com:8988/upload/vod/2019-08-11/201908111565523427.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">8.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">40集全/已完结</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/97811/">赛尔号第二季</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E7%BD%97%E7%8E%89%E5%A9%B7------------/" target="_blank">罗玉婷</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%9D%8E%E6%99%94------------/" target="_blank">李晔</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E7%8E%8B%E7%AB%A0%E4%BF%8A--------/" target="_blank">王章俊</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/4/" target="_blank">动漫</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86-----------/" target="_blank">大陆</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2012/" target="_blank">2012</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.08.12</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>《赛尔号之圣者逆袭》是《赛尔号》动画片的续集讲述的是2110年，地球能源已接近枯竭，环境污染日趋严重。 为了实现地外星系探索计划，人类制造了名为赛尔的机器人，并建造能源探索飞船赛尔号，寻找传说中的无尽能源。可就在找到无尽能源的时候，无尽能源被宇宙海盗欧比组织摧毁，赛尔们不得不去寻找藏在宇宙深处，由谱</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/97811/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/4835/" data-original="http://pic.iqiyi6123.com/upload/vod/2019-01-17/15477120144.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">8.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center"></span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/4835/">赛尔号大电影2之雷伊与迈尔斯</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E6%AD%A6%E8%89%BA------------/" target="_blank">武艺</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%BC%A0%E6%9D%B0------------/" target="_blank">张杰</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%9B%BE%E8%BD%B6%E5%8F%AF------------/" target="_blank">曾轶可</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E7%8E%8B%E7%AB%A0%E4%BF%8A--------/" target="_blank">王章俊</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-----%E4%BB%98%E6%9D%B0--------/" target="_blank">付杰</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/22/" target="_blank">其他片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86-----------/" target="_blank">大陆</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2012/" target="_blank">2012</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.08.07</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>宇宙海盗抓获了圣灵系神兽精灵迈尔斯，迈尔斯在被捕前将幻影宝石交给儿子蒙塔，将它送出了幻影星 圣灵系迈尔斯的求救惊动了远在赫尔卡星的雷伊，雷伊迅速做出了反应前往了幻影星。 被海盗追击的蒙塔闯入赛尔号，并意外帮助赛小息赢得赛尔号一年一度的精灵大师杯的选拔赛。得知蒙塔的身世后，赛小息决定和队友阿铁打、卡璐</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/4835/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/85519/" data-original="http://cj.subo8988.com:8988/upload/vod/2019-07-04/201907041562229733.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">6.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">更新至05集</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/85519/">赛尔号第10季：冰封要塞</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span>未知</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span>未知</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/4/" target="_blank">动漫</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86-----------/" target="_blank">大陆</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2019/" target="_blank">2019</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>为了解决地球能源危机，赛尔号肩负着在太空中发现新能源的使命，在一次又一次的任务中，为地球输送了宝贵的宇宙数据和清洁能源，而现在主人公SPT小队又将展开新的探索冒险之旅，他们下一个目的地会是哪里呢？在航行途中赛尔号被一种名为‘寒冰’的结界挡住了去路，为了打开结界，SPT先锋小队来到冰雪星，在这里将会遇</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/85519/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/71369/" data-original="http://cj.subo8988.com:8988/upload/vod/2019-02-09/201902091549650076.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">5.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">HD</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/71369/">赛尔号大电影5：雷神崛起</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E7%BD%97%E7%8E%89%E5%A9%B7------------/" target="_blank">罗玉婷</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E7%BF%9F%E5%B7%8D------------/" target="_blank">翟巍</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E7%8E%8B%E6%99%93%E5%BD%A4------------/" target="_blank">王晓彤</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%AD%99%E6%99%94------------/" target="_blank">孙晔</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%90%B4%E7%A3%8A------------/" target="_blank">吴磊</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E8%92%8B%E5%8F%AF------------/" target="_blank">蒋可</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%88%98%E5%8C%97%E8%BE%B0------------/" target="_blank">刘北辰</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%9D%8E%E6%99%94------------/" target="_blank">李晔</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E7%8E%8B%E7%AB%A0%E4%BF%8A--------/" target="_blank">王章俊</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/4/" target="_blank">动漫</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86-----------/" target="_blank">大陆</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2015/" target="_blank">2015</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>几经争战之后，战神联盟在赫尔卡星建立了一座“雷霆守护局”,守护三座圣塔和星球子民某天赫尔卡星突然出现了一位巨型意外来客，伤害无辜精灵，企图摧毁城市。战神联盟火速集结，在调查幕后真凶的过程中，雷伊与大反派奥古斯塔博士相遇，交战中，雷伊发现了同胞哥哥的遇难之谜，但也中计受伤，被奥古斯塔激发了体内的邪恶力</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/71369/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/18597/" data-original="http://cj.subo8988.com:8988/upload/vod/2018-11-02/201811021541138112.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">4.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">HD</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/18597/">赛尔号大电影6：圣者无敌</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E7%BD%97%E7%8E%89%E5%A9%B7------------/" target="_blank">罗玉婷</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E7%BF%9F%E5%B7%8D------------/" target="_blank">翟巍</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E7%8E%8B%E6%99%93%E5%BD%A4------------/" target="_blank">王晓彤</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%AD%99%E6%99%94------------/" target="_blank">孙晔</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E7%8E%8B%E7%AB%A0%E4%BF%8A--------/" target="_blank">王章俊</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-------------/" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/4/" target="_blank">动漫</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86-----------/" target="_blank">大陆</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2017/" target="_blank">2017</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>从前，在神秘森林里有个外星小孩儿，他带着面具，机灵古怪，终日与吹泡泡的毛猴儿们为伴某日，一群凶残至极的鲨齿狼冲进森林，只见头狼身上坐着宇宙精灵捕手克拉，与正在寻找圣者谱尼的SPT队员们撞个正着。一场上天入地的激战就此展开！一路上SPT队员们偶遇食人鲨、野猪、圣光彩蝶、闪光比波、利牙鱼、蘑菇怪……孰敌</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/18597/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/49883/" data-original="https://img.tupian-zuida.com/pic/upload/vod/2018-06-08/201806081528441768.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">3.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">30集全</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/49883/">赛尔号 第9季</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E5%86%85%E8%AF%A6------------/" target="_blank">内详</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E6%9C%AA%E7%9F%A5--------/" target="_blank">未知</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/4/" target="_blank">动漫</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86-----------/" target="_blank">大陆</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2018/" target="_blank">2018</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>赛尔号第九季《霹雳九重天》主要讲述了赛尔号飞船在前往飞龙座星系的途中意外误入了逆世界空间的故事</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/49883/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><div class="fed-page-info fed-text-center"><a class="fed-btns-info fed-rims-info fed-hide fed-show-xs-inline fed-btns-disad" href="/s/%E8%B5%9B%E5%B0%94%E5%8F%B7------------/">首页</a><a class="fed-btns-info fed-rims-info fed-btns-disad" href="/s/%E8%B5%9B%E5%B0%94%E5%8F%B7------------/">上页</a><a class="fed-btns-in